{
  "version": 2,
  "_doc": "Synthetic fixture set for the relative-path-wrong-CWD branch of the excel-activities/read-range-file-not-found playbook. Agent must chain: folders list-current-user → jobs list --state Faulted → jobs get (resolved path shows %LocalAppData%\\UiPath\\Packages\\... prefix) → jobs logs → workflow source. The combination of (relative WorkbookPath in source) + (per-package prefix in resolved path) is decisive.",
